      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantBackgroundService",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantBackgroundService.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for tenant-aware hosted services (<xref href=\"Microsoft.Extensions.Hosting.IHostedService\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>).\nOverride <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantBackgroundService.ExecuteForTenantAsync(AspNetCore.Multitenancy.ITenantContext%2cSystem.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to implement per-tenant logic.\nThe base class iterates all active tenants and calls your method in a scoped tenant context.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobActivator.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobActivator.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobActivator",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobActivator.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Resolves Hangfire job instances from a per-tenant DI scope, ensuring that\nany scoped services (including <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.ITenantContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>) are resolved\nfrom the correct tenant scope.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobFilter.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobFilter.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobFilter",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobFilter.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Hangfire server filter that automatically propagates tenant context into background jobs.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobFilter.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"3\">On enqueue: serializes the current <code>TenantId</code> into the Hangfire job parameters.\nOn execute: reads <code>TenantId</code> from job params, creates a tenant DI scope,\nsets <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.ITenantContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, then executes the job in that scope.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantJobFilter.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"7\">Register once in Program.cs — jobs see a fully populated ITenantContext identical\nto an HTTP request context.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.BackgroundJobs.TenantRecurringJobManager.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
