      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.ITenantEntity",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.ITenantEntity.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Marks an entity as tenant-scoped. The EF Core model builder and\n<xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> use this interface to apply global query\nfilters and to stamp <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.ITenantEntity.TenantId\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> on insert automatically.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base <xref href=\"Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.DbContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for multi-tenant applications.\nAutomatically:</p>\n<ul><li>Applies global query filters for all <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.ITenantEntity\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> entity types</li><li>Stamps <code>TenantId</code> on every insert via <code>SaveChanges</code></li><li>Sets the default schema from <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.ITenantContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for schema-per-tenant strategy</li></ul>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"6\">Inherit from this class in your application DbContext.</p>\n"
    },
