      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.DbPerTenantStrategy",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.DbPerTenantStrategy.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Isolation strategy: each tenant has a completely separate SQL Server/PostgreSQL database.\nMaximum isolation. Recommended for enterprise and regulated tenants.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.DbPerTenantStrategy.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"4\">Usage in Program.cs:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">builder.Services.AddDbContext&lt;AppDbContext&gt;((sp, opts) =&gt;\n    DbPerTenantStrategy.Configure(opts, sp));</code></pre>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.RowLevelStrategy.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.RowLevelStrategy.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.RowLevelStrategy",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.RowLevelStrategy.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Isolation strategy: all tenants share tables. Every table has a <code>TenantId</code> column.\nEF Core global query filters automatically scope all queries.\nCheapest to operate. Recommended for low-risk SaaS.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.RowLevelStrategy.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\">This strategy is applied automatically by <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.MultitenantDbContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nEntities must implement <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.ITenantEntity\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.SchemaPerTenantStrategy.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.SchemaPerTenantStrategy.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.SchemaPerTenantStrategy",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.SchemaPerTenantStrategy.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Isolation strategy: all tenants share one database but each gets a dedicated schema\n(e.g., <code>acme.Products</code>, <code>globex.Products</code>).\nGood balance of isolation vs cost.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.EntityFrameworkCore.Strategies.SchemaPerTenantStrategy.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\">The schema is taken from <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.TenantInfo.Schema\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>. If not set, falls back to\n<xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.TenantInfo.Id\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
