      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.RequireFeatureAttribute",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.RequireFeatureAttribute.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Marks a controller or action as requiring a specific tenant feature.\nIf the feature is disabled for the current tenant's plan, the middleware\nreturns HTTP 404 (not 403) so that other tenants cannot enumerate which\nfeatures exist.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantFeatureMiddleware.yml",
