      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantFeatureMiddleware",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantFeatureMiddleware.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Middleware that checks <xref href=\"AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.RequireFeatureAttribute\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> on the matched endpoint\nand returns HTTP 404 if the feature is disabled for the current tenant's plan.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantFeatureMiddleware.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"4\">Returns 404 (not 403) deliberately — so tenants cannot enumerate which features exist\non other plans.</p>\n"
    },
