      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantPlanFeatureProvider",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantPlanFeatureProvider.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Maps subscription plan names to sets of enabled features.\nConfigure the plan → feature mapping at startup.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/AspNetCore.Multitenancy.FeatureFlags.TenantPlanFeatureProvider.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"4\">Example:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">services.Configure&lt;PlanFeatureOptions&gt;(opts =&gt;\n{\n    opts.AddPlan(\"free\",       new[] { \"BasicDashboard\" });\n    opts.AddPlan(\"pro\",        new[] { \"BasicDashboard\", \"AdvancedReporting\", \"ApiAccess\" });\n    opts.AddPlan(\"enterprise\", new[] { \"BasicDashboard\", \"AdvancedReporting\", \"ApiAccess\", \"WhiteLabel\", \"SSOIntegration\" });\n});</code></pre>\n"
    },
